Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Banga Central Elementary School in the Municipality of Banga, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Jose A. Urquiola Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 735
An Act Changing the Name of the Banga Central Elementary School in the Municipality of Banga, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Jose A. Urquiola Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Banga Central Elementary School located in the Municipality of Banga, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Honorable Jose A. Urquiola Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
